<number box="[510,524,1719,1745]" pageId="3" pageNumber="22" value="3.0">3</number>
promarginal and 
<number box="[735,750,1719,1745]" pageId="3" pageNumber="22" value="2.0">2</number>
retromarginal teeth (
<figureCitation box="[1000,1073,1719,1745]" captionStart="FIGURES 9 – 12" captionStartId="4.[151,269,1461,1485]" captionTargetBox="[155,1425,265,1402]" captionTargetId="figure@4.[151,1436,258,1438]" captionTargetPageId="4" captionText="FIGURES 9 – 12. Draconarius expansus spec. nov. male, 9. Cheliceral teeth, ventral view; 10. Pedipalpus, retrolateral view; 11. Ditto, ventral view; 12. Ditto, prolateral view. Scale bar: 0.2 mm." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/182479/files/figure.png" pageId="3" pageNumber="22">
Fig. 
<number box="[1056,1073,1719,1745]" pageId="3" pageNumber="22" value="9.0">9</number>
</figureCitation>
). Leg formula unknown; measurements of legs: I: 
<number box="[396,433,1759,1785]" pageId="3" pageNumber="22" value="8.4">8.4</number>
(
<number box="[449,489,1759,1785]" pageId="3" pageNumber="22" value="2.4">2.4</number>
